<h1 id="overlay-title">C&C: Red Alert 2</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The intro sequence in Command &amp; Conquer: Red Alert 2 shows the Soviet Union launching a surprise invasion of the United States.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="qe189o">
